data.description: Nestled on a corner lot, this 3-bed, 2-bath home is a stylish haven with modern comforts. Open living spaces bask in natural light, connecting the living, dining, and kitchen areas seamlessly. The kitchen features quartz countertops and stainless steel appliances, while the bedrooms offer peaceful retreats. Step outside to the expansive backyard for outdoor enjoyment. Conveniently located near schools and shopping, this home is a blend of convenience and charm. New carpet and padding being installed!      This is a perfect opportunity for a first time home buyer or an investor! SELLER FINANCING AVAILABLE! NO CREDIT, NO CREDENTIALS, NO ORIGINATION FEES! Here are the terms: $105k down payment (28%); seller finances the balance of $270K mortgage at 3.99% (30 year amortization) with a monthly payment of $1,418.47 including solar panel and HOA (this does not include taxes and insurance escrow).     STR not permitted per HOA.
